latestPosts.caption:
Finally I am graduating…
It feels like yesterday when I entered the gates of this prestigious institution thinking that it’s a dream. Miranda became my safe space, a place I can call home, I’m not ready to say goodbye yet but with a heavy heart and uncountable memories and lessons I’ll move on to the next chapter of my life. 
Thank you for shaping me into the person I am today and giving me the most genuine friends.
From an all girl’s school to an all women’s college I wouldn’t have it any other way.
Forever grateful ♾️ 

.
